title: Tour de France star fined for kissing wife
description: A Tour de France rider has apologised after wild scenes erupted during a time trial when he stopped to kiss his wife.

title: ‘Shocked’: Cyclist dead after horrific incident
description: The cycling world has ben left “shocked and heartbroken” over the death of a 25-year-old rider following a sickening incident.

title: Insane detail as Tour de France record broken
description: Mark Cavendish is the toast of the cycling world after the sprinter finally broke an iconic Tour de France record, rewriting the history books.

title: ‘Sacrifice’ needed for Aussie’s Tour success
description: The Tour de France starts this weekend and Australia’s only winner has explained why the chances of another Aussie victory may have to wait.

title: Weird way America is rigging medal tally
description: Americans reading about the Olympics have a “shameless” take on which country is on top of the medal tally in Paris.

title: ‘Giant step’: Firebirds name new coach
description: The struggling Queensland Firebirds have turned to a former New Zealand under-21 coach to revive their fortunes.

title: Olympics eyesore infuriates Kelly Slater
description: Surfing legend Kelly Slater has torn the Olympics to shreds over a controversial sight at the Paris Games’ surfing site.
